scenes.description: Performance of the song 'SHINKIRO' by Houshou Marine, Shiranui Flare, Moona Hoshinova, and Gawr Gura.
Performance of the song 'HELP!!' by Kobo Kanaeru, Omaru Polka, and Hakos Baelz.
Performance of the song 'Holo Hawk' by Takanashi Kiara, Sakura Miko, Pavolia Reine, and Anya Melfissa.
